commit.message:
Changed OCTAVES constant from 8 to 9.

Octaves in this system are counted from 0 to use a low reference frequency, so 9 octaves are needed to account for octaves 0 through 8.
Minor change (fixed line of more than 80 characters)
Added sample code for Mongo connect
Added a list of Python packages and brief summaries of each.

Created sandbox.py

Created a file "sandbox.py" for prototyping and demoing purposes.
